      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I AM HELLBOUND (9) brings strong form from Menangle where he has won four of his last five outings, beating Inter Dominion hopefuls when he raced parked but toughed out a narrow win in the G3 Yamamoto Trotters Mile last week. Cops a back row draw but he is good enough to overcome that and beat these. SUPERIOR STRIDE (3) is a progressive three-year-old who has recorded three easy wins along with a 4m fifth in the NSW Trotters Derby from his last four outings in Sydney. Has led from wider barriers to cruise home in his last two appearances so can give a big sight from this draw. RAFFIE JAY NZ (1) is a lightly-raced former Kiwi filly who has easily won her two starts here since crossing the Tasman. This is stronger but she gets the ace draw and has upside. FREDIDRIVSAMERCURY (4) is another stepping up in class but he is progressing nicely having won his last three outings at this circuit and distance.",
